From 30710cabbcbf9da375b247dd9cf2add577ed9256 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: grok-build-providers-verify <verify@invalid>
Date: Mon, 20 Jul 2026 19:13:11 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 15/16] Improve Codex parallel tool-call handling

Force parallel_tool_calls on Responses/Codex requests, preserve
Responses function-call item ids as call_id|fc_id for history replay,
and commit local tool results in assistant source order while tools
still execute concurrently.
